import React, { Component } from 'react' export class Qhse extends Component { render() { return (

QHSE

Clockwise Technologies is BSI registered firm, where quality is paramount and where we take care and exceptional pride in all the articles that we manufacture.

With a fully endorsed management system to ISO 9001:2015 we maintain a robust adherence to all matters of quality and applicable standards.

“Metal fabrication, machining, design, equipment sales and associated product testing for surface and sub-surface equipment for the energy sector”

Each enquiry is dealt with in the same manner regardless of the project size and everything is allocated a unique tracking code that follows it all the way through design, manufacture, deliver and archive.

At Clockwise we do not operate a statute of time over records, so all projects or enquiries are stored and can be digitally accessed at anytime, and even remotely from our customers own office.

) } } export default Qhse
